{
  "texts": [
    "This means schedulers are able to go back in time, monitor the present in (near) real time or simulate future operations.",
    "For the automated terminal Yangshan Phase 4 in Shanghai, mainly (near) real-time data from the ECS (Equipment Control System) is used.",
    "However, sensor data typically used for maintenance is not included and could potentially improve the models.",
    "In comparison, Dalian container terminals do not yet include data from IoT devices, but otherwise the models are similar.",
    "The manual terminals at the Port of Dalian, operated with RTGs, do not yet utilize a strict digital twin."
  ]
}